Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.00,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}翻译：鸡柳 はばやし　校对：はばやし　后期：傻瓜三世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十六艘东舞鹤教员舰都丧失了航行能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道说 武藏号真的叛乱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这份报告不能说明问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号受损轻微 晴风号不得不撤离战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无法追踪目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}教员舰搭载的都是尖端设备 为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为电子设备和追踪导弹全都产生了故障
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船员怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三重紧急装置可不是摆设
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无人死亡 另有少数人轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号还剩多少燃料和弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出航时是按最大容量补给的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以推测燃料和弹药应当都还剩八成以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要补给到满
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为在海上为大和级舰船提供补给比较困难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}校长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比睿号 鸟海号失去了联络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}除了武藏号以外 还有哪些舰船位置不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比睿号 鸟海号 摩耶号 五十铃号 名取号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天津风号 矶风号 时津风号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有来自德国 原计划参加演习的海军上将施佩伯爵号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么多？现在哪些船能接受调度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正在执行补给任务的间宫号 明石号 风早号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有她们的护卫舰 秋风号 浜风号 舞风号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有执行侦察任务的长良号 晴风号 浦风号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}荻风号 谷风号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}山城号 加贺号 赤城号 伊吹号 生驹号正在修理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}情况再紧急 半年以内也无法出动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海舰可以优先修理 但至少也要花三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能派去武藏号失联地点的有哪些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号之外的船都去搜索其他舰船了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少这几天无法调度
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:11.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}静かに燃える世界　始まりはここから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:15.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}夜空が終わりを告げるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:21.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}ひとすじの光が　胸に秘めた声が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:25.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}解き放つ　闇を裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:30.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}枯れるよりいっそ　散り急ぐ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:35.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迷い　歩く術を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:43.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}千の波に　呑まれた心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}君さえ守れない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:51.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}響け確かな衝動　鳴り止まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:56.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忘れられぬ傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:01.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今もかすかな残像　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:06.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界が待ってる　明日の産声を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:11.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}響け確かな衝動　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:19.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}そう未来と過去が交差する　百年目の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【OPCN】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:11.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一切都始于这个静静地燃烧着的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:15.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在长夜将明的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:21.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一道光芒 一声发自灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:25.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}冲破束缚 撕裂黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:30.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}寻求着归宿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:35.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迷茫地迈足前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:43.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这颗被波涛掩去的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至没法保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:51.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}心脏在胸中激荡 就像要跳出来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:56.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}留下无法忘却的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:01.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}希望这微弱的残影 永远不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:06.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界正在等待 属于明日的婴啼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:11.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}心脏在胸中激荡 千万不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:19.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的 这是一首交错着过去与未来的百年长歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么有你这种成天抛开自己的船不管的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是说海上的伙伴们都是一家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这艘船上的船员难道不是你的家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是不是真的不适合做舰长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回收完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全身都湿透了 当心感冒啊 去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就知道我们的舰长肯定不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胜田同学 现在我们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只顾得上逃跑了 根本没时间记录方位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}报告受损情况 确认周边情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无法确认前方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无法确认左舷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右舷也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷达一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无法接收信号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}声呐里什么也听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别这么异口同声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}电子设备好像都不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像受到了原因不明的电磁干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在观测星空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开始天文测量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.37,Post,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(644,54)\c&HF9F6F7&}轮机科
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.37,Post,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\c&H555ED3&\bord0\an1\pos(361.6,429.2)}·别忘东西·垃圾入箱\N·节约用水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.37,Post,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\c&H7E685A&\bord0\pos(792.4,399.6)}洗浴完毕后\N切记转动执勤表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.37,Post,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\c&H4B5F65&\3c&HAFFFFE&\pos(640,578)}浴室是让各位休息的地方。\N注意保持整洁。——卫生委员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}方位已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}北纬35度15分29秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东经136度4分35秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在我们在…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}报告情况时要迅速准确
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在琵琶湖的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来 我们在琵琶湖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 现在那里通水路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就说怎么这么风平浪静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我们重新测量一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出了一身臭汗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶快洗个澡清爽清爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 舰长 现在是轮机科洗澡的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一舰之长不遵守规矩 这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干啥呢 干啥呢 吵啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长？你浑身都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常时刻管它什么规矩不规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们也别干看着了 快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东舞鹤教员舰因武藏号的攻击丧失了航行能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然还是学生叛乱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}万一武藏号跑去了浮舟都市 她们有能力制止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根据晴风号的报告 追踪导弹会发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能通过大量鱼雷或者集中炮火制止她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号上的都是成绩优秀的学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无追踪能力的鱼雷想在武藏射程外命中目标有那么简单？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恐怕很难 那么只能用同样的装备去应对她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}18英寸主炮对18英寸主炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过吴港的大和号和舞鹤港的信浓号都在维修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}佐世保港的纪伊号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 它远航地球的另一面 回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}14英寸主炮和16英寸主炮拿它无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这次是把5英寸主炮换成了3.9英寸主炮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}5英寸主炮也有它的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉真不错 真希望老夫船上也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可是晴风号60000马力烧出来的特色澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}维护起来可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那孩子就是爱耍脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊是啊 而且最后还是得降低功率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这高压发动机还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰桥总是下达全速前进的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}于是舰长 上边发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上边？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们这些烧火的压根不知道外头发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能这种时候问问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 东舞鹤的教员舰和武藏号交战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号？就是我们学校那艘？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东舞鹤？不就是上次那潜艇的学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}教员舰搭载的都是尖端设备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也被老师打过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以她们也是遇上了那种状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 所以我才想制止她们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这个舰长居然又一马当先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一艘跳艇怎么可能制止得了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道除了你就没人可去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有句话说得好「神舆要轻 里头抬着个笨蛋最好」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.93,Remark,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}注：1982年小泽一郎在自民党总裁选举时说的话。虽然和原句略有出入，但基本意思差不多。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷 装甲编号135
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水线附近有个20cm乘50cm的豁口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轻微泄漏出一些柴油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 这个伤口可不小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.98,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}清爽清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洗澡就是愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很担心武藏号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号的舰长是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏号到底怎么了 她们怎样才能获救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}担心别人之前不该先担心一下自家的船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也许武藏号舰长也和施佩号舰长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想独自保护好自己的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩号舰长西娅 总是能当机立断 是个很厉害的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果舰长觉得害怕 船员也都会害怕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以舰长必须把畏惧藏在心中 独自挑起重担
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是她的原话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还远远比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是救下了老夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫能站在这里 也都得感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 还鼓励了总是逃来逃去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打扰一下 舰长 有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚才开始就一直接不到信号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是船内捕捉到了微弱的电波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是手机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得去看看 带我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 舰桥交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个能探测出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}测不出来吧 这种东西怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是这？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是美波同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好小 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五十六真厉害 抓到老鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 颜色有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接收到信号了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷达恢复运转 这下什么都能探测到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}附近的声音听上去很清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来它就是罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它的基因和老鼠有一点点区别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且感染了一种奇怪的病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炮术长的血液里面也检查出了这种病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}病毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炮术长会失去理智 电子设备会故障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能都是它搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要研究一下它 就能救回同学们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五十六好厉害 大功一件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天开始就叫你提督吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大提督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能随便给提督头衔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要紧的难道不是赶快汇报学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前方发现漂浮物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像在云端一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}令人感动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是附近漂满了水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}捅着捅着不会爆炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些都是旧式的触发水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别碰到凸起部分就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把它们全都引爆不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾太浓了 看不清周围到底有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是发生了连锁反应那就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚上的时候 我用声呐侦测了周边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}布雷范围有多广
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}布雷目的应该是阻断航线 范围比较狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然不知道是哪种水雷 但是考虑到周边水深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是锚雷 短锚雷和沉底雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}锚雷是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是那种用线拉着雷锭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有东西撞上就会轰隆一声爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来需要扫扫雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么扫雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先把扫雷具挂在扫索上 然后把展开器沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}随着船只的前进 展开器会向两侧展开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰尾拉着定深器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是扫索挂到了水雷 就会拉动割刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咔嚓一下剪断雷索
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后用机枪扫射浮上来的水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轮到我登场了 快让我开几枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在我们周边都是水雷 不能贸然前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有扫雷具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船上没有真正的扫雷具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但总该做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水下人工除雷很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用「跳艇」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个很小 很难引爆音响 水压 磁性等各种水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}除了普通设备 还要让乘坐的人装备紧急装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长就不要下海了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明娜同学 你不喜欢吃纳豆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没 没啊 怎么会惹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咬舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咬舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实我吃不惯日本菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗 不好意思没考虑到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不今天我做德国菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用了不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事的 我很会做德国菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 今天的正餐就吃德国菜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.08,Post,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H68BB67&\frz19.39\an4\pos(299.2,670.4)}连德国人都会感到惊艳。\N北德菜之王德国猪脚！\N只要用高压锅就能轻松地做出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}周边水雷分部情况侦测完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准备扫雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不扫雷怎么安全地航行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先解决可视范围内的水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 终于轮到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我来 小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快感 手感 成吉思感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说 起个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}画的是海豹 就叫小玉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs40\pos(801.6,648.8)}多摩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.38,Remark,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}注：小玉，2002-2004年出现在多摩川的一只海豹。当时受到闲着没事做的日本媒体广泛报道。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这水雷会是谁施放的呢 多危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}历史上施放在这里的水雷穿越时空复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失在马尾藻海的水雷居然出现在了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这一定是某国的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阴谋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这一带的水雷应该是各国为了保护本国利益
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以及防卫海上交通线而施放的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}20世纪初的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现实一点也不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}战争这种东西真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝色人鱼就是为了避免战争 超越国界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}共同守护大海而成立的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝色人鱼的主要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是救援 扫雷等保护航线的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与海同生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与海共存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}面朝大海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是蓝色人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定要注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开始扫雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白 全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别开太快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小理 水雷浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 我们继…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前方水下发生爆炸 波及了跳艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收到求援信号了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有两个信号 是紧急装置发射的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快去救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这个舰长又打算擅离职守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 和我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 舰桥就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}诶 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听令 一切优先本舰安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}万里小路同学 仔细侦测一下有没有其他水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长应该留在舰桥指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这才叫always on the deck吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能接受逃来逃去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道什么样的舰长才算理想的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 我很庆幸 我们的舰长是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你 小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 我这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在扫雷来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起来了 这是紧急装置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小理 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会有人来救我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会有的吧 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小代 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来 抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小理 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救援成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 说到德国菜肯定是这个 德国猪脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是北德的菜 我们那边的是德国烤猪脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般来说都是用烤的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没 没事 还有一道经典菜 德国爽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}德国酸菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且这只是醋腌卷心菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般来说应该加酸发酵的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有 肉排
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是猪排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肉排是德国菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炸肉排啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在德国肉排没这么厚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吧 这是压轴大菜 最有名的德国菜 汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是肉丸吗 这种菜在德国不常见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过蒸土豆和大锅菜看上去挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出航在外 要是有德国香肠的话老夫就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些是谁做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃 好好吃 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:47.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,531.333)}多灾多难的扫雷行动！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:54.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:22:00.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:06.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:23.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:29.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:36.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:44.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:53.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:57.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:01.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:07.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:11.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:16.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\3c&HD7C392&\c&HFAF7EF&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【EDCN】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:54.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}青色七洋 今天也环绕着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:22:00.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}我会比话语还要温柔 轻轻地推着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:06.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}是啊 这就是你和我之间的涟漪效应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:23.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}面前的惊涛骇浪 一浪卷来一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:29.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们选择的航路 就是我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:36.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}如果你忘记了微笑 我会笑给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:44.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}流过眼泪之后 让坚强随波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:53.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}青色七洋 今天也环绕着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:57.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}比话语还要温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:01.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是这片晴空和习习凉风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:07.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描绘梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:11.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我希望我就是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:16.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\3c&HD7C392&\c&HFAF7EF&}要相信春天正在等待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姑且做了几份抗体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是没效那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知之不若行之 学至于行而止矣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手 美波同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是发生了什么 记得制止我
